1. As a steam Web API user, I want a consistent and easy to use interface to the API, so that my developement time and cost is reduced.

2. As a steam Web API user, I want the rules for interaction with the API to be abstracted, so that I don't need to be concerned with the details and can concentrate on my developement.

3. As a steam Web API user, I want to persist some data, so that my response time is reduced.

